      <div style="margin-top:12px" class="lead-text" id="guideContent">
<strong>Productivity Boost Blueprint — 5 Rituals for Clean Mental Energy</strong>

1) Morning Clarity Ritual
- 60–90 minutes after waking: hydrate + 1 light protein snack.
- Single nootropic pouch (if you use caffeine) to start focused tasks for 60–90 minutes.
- 10 minutes of zero-distraction deep work (use a timer).

2) Midday Reset
- If afternoon drag appears: short walk (7–10 minutes) + 1 Energy pouch only if needed.
- Avoid pairing with heavy carbs that spike then crash.

3) Micro-Rituals During Work Sprints
- 25–45 minute focused sprints with 5–10 min breaks.
- Use a single pouch at start of difficult sprints — mind the 2–3 hour gap rule.

4) Evening Wind-Down (No-caffeine)
- Stop stimulants at least 6 hours before planned sleep.
- Use the Zero pouch for ritual without caffeine if desired.

5) Weekly Review
- Track which sessions felt best (note mood, focus, and sleep).
- Reduce or pause pouches if sleep is affected.

Tips:
- Start with one pouch per day if you are caffeine sensitive.
- Always check ingredient labels and consult a healthcare provider for medical concerns.
- Try Nectr with intention — pair pouches with a small routine and measure changes.

Thanks for trying the guide — hit "Download" to save a local copy.
